Servlet API

Copy the Servlet API jar from your favorite Servlet container here -
  for Apache Tomcat, cp {tomcat.home}/common/lib/servlet-api.jar .
  for Sun App Server, cp {sunappserver.home}/lib/j2ee.jar .
  for Jetty, cp {jetty.home}/lib/javax.servlet.jar .

